{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/shader_programming_intro_4/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>본 포스팅은 Pope Kim의 『셰이더 프로그래밍 입문 (한빛미디어, 2012)』의 Part 1의 Chapter 4에 해당하는 내용(p. 93-107)을 요약하기 위해 작성되었다.</p>\n<h2>학습 목표</h2>\n<p>셰이더를 통해 난반사광 조명셰이더를 구현하고 이 원리를 이해한다.</p>\n<h2>난반사광 조명셰이더 구현하기</h2>\n<p>편의를 위해 \"<a href=\"https://sungkukpark.github.io/shader_programming_intro_2/\">진짜 쉬운 빨강 셰이더</a>\"의 완성 시점부터 난반사광 조명셰이더를 구현해보자. 만약 아직 렌더몽키와 HLSL 기초 문법을 숙지하지 못했다면 링크된 페이지를 참조해 앞선 튜토리얼을 먼저 따라해보도록 한다.</p>\n<h3>개발 환경 설정: 입사광의 벡터와 표면법선벡터 추가</h3>\n<p>우선 Workspace 창의 프로젝트 이름을 \"ColorShader\"에서 \"LightingShaderDiffuse\"로 변경한다.</p>\n<h4>입사광 벡터 추가</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>입사광 벡터 역할을 월드 광원의 위치를 전역 변수로 추가한다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a5f8073670f81d1278ff8c6f15da22ec/9b29b/add_world_light_position.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"add_world_light_position\"\n        title=\"add_world_light_position\"\n        src=\"/static/a5f8073670f81d1278ff8c6f15da22ec/5a190/add_world_light_position.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a5f8073670f81d1278ff8c6f15da22ec/772e8/add_world_light_position.png 200w,\n/static/a5f8073670f81d1278ff8c6f15da22ec/e17e5/add_world_light_position.png 400w,\n/static/a5f8073670f81d1278ff8c6f15da22ec/5a190/add_world_light_position.png 800w,\n/static/a5f8073670f81d1278ff8c6f15da22ec/c1b63/add_world_light_position.png 1200w,\n/static/a5f8073670f81d1278ff8c6f15da22ec/29007/add_world_light_position.png 1600w,\n/static/a5f8073670f81d1278ff8c6f15da22ec/9b29b/add_world_light_position.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol>\n<li>해당 월드 광원의 위치값으로 <code class=\"language-text\">(500, 500, -500, 1)</code>을 대입한다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d68c54fe82109e0461b1ff5e57996ef7/9b29b/assign_world_light_position_value.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"assign_world_light_position_value\"\n        title=\"assign_world_light_position_value\"\n        src=\"/static/d68c54fe82109e0461b1ff5e57996ef7/5a190/assign_world_light_position_value.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d68c54fe82109e0461b1ff5e57996ef7/772e8/assign_world_light_position_value.png 200w,\n/static/d68c54fe82109e0461b1ff5e57996ef7/e17e5/assign_world_light_position_value.png 400w,\n/static/d68c54fe82109e0461b1ff5e57996ef7/5a190/assign_world_light_position_value.png 800w,\n/static/d68c54fe82109e0461b1ff5e57996ef7/c1b63/assign_world_light_position_value.png 1200w,\n/static/d68c54fe82109e0461b1ff5e57996ef7/29007/assign_world_light_position_value.png 1600w,\n/static/d68c54fe82109e0461b1ff5e57996ef7/9b29b/assign_world_light_position_value.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4>표면법선 벡터 추가</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\"Stream Mapping\" 항목을 더블 클릭한 뒤 \"Add\" 버튼을 통해 Usage를 \"NORMAL\", Data Type을 \"FLOAT3\"로 갖는 항목을 추가한다</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5dafd39af5de6b8d6734b45870922057/9b29b/add_normal_vector.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"add_normal_vector\"\n        title=\"add_normal_vector\"\n        src=\"/static/5dafd39af5de6b8d6734b45870922057/5a190/add_normal_vector.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5dafd39af5de6b8d6734b45870922057/772e8/add_normal_vector.png 200w,\n/static/5dafd39af5de6b8d6734b45870922057/e17e5/add_normal_vector.png 400w,\n/static/5dafd39af5de6b8d6734b45870922057/5a190/add_normal_vector.png 800w,\n/static/5dafd39af5de6b8d6734b45870922057/c1b63/add_normal_vector.png 1200w,\n/static/5dafd39af5de6b8d6734b45870922057/29007/add_normal_vector.png 1600w,\n/static/5dafd39af5de6b8d6734b45870922057/9b29b/add_normal_vector.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>정점 셰이더 함수 구현: 람베르트 모델을 사용해 난반사광을 계산한 뒤 반환</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"hlsl\"><pre class=\"language-hlsl\"><code class=\"language-hlsl\"><span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">VS_INPUT</span> \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> POSITION<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float3</span> mNormal <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> NORMAL<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">VS_OUTPUT</span> \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> POSITION<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float3</span> mDiffuse <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> TEXCOORD1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">float4x4</span> gWorldMatrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">float4x4</span> gViewMatrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">float4x4</span> gProjectionMatrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> gWorldLightPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nVS_OUTPUT <span class=\"token function\">vs_main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> VS_INPUT Input <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   VS_OUTPUT Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Input<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gWorldMatrix <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>         <span class=\"token comment\">// 월드 행렬로 공간 변환</span>\n   \n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float3</span> lightDir <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>xyz <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> gWorldLightPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>xyz<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   lightDir <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">normalize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> lightDir <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   \n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gViewMatrix <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>          <span class=\"token comment\">// 뷰 행렬로 공간 변환</span>\n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mPosition<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gProjectionMatrix <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// 투영 행렬로 공간 변환</span>\n   \n   <span class=\"token keyword\">float3</span> worldNormal <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mul</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Input<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mNormal<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">float3x3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>gWorldMatrix <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   worldNormal <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">normalize</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> worldNormal <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   \n   Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mDiffuse <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">dot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span> lightDir<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> worldNormal <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   \n   <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> Output<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3>픽셀 셰이더 함수 구현: 난반사광 값을 반환</h3>\n<p>여기서 픽셀 셰이더 함수가 하는 일은 정점 셰이더에서 전달된 난반사광 값을 그대로 반환하는 정도다. 단, 여기서 <a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/direct3dhlsl/dx-graphics-hlsl-saturate\">saturate HLSL 함수</a>는 특정 값을 0에서 1 사이의 값으로 고정하는 함수이다. 즉, 0보다 작은 값은 0으로, 1보다 작은 값은 1로 고정한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"hlsl\"><pre class=\"language-hlsl\"><code class=\"language-hlsl\"><span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PS_INPUT</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">float3</span> mDiffuse <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> TEXCOORD1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span> <span class=\"token function\">ps_main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> PS_INPUT Input <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> COLOR\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">float3</span> diffuse <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">saturate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Input<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mDiffuse <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">float4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>diffuse<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>완성된 난반사광 조명셰이더 예제</h3>\n<p>마침내 난반사광 조명셰이더가 적용된 셰이더가 완성되었다. 다들 각자 생애 첫 난반사광 조명셰이더를 구현한 기쁨을 만끽하도록 하자</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f09cdbe3746c7fadf665fd9ce1c76e8a/9b29b/lighting_shader_diffuse_completed.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lighting_shader_diffuse_completed\"\n        title=\"lighting_shader_diffuse_completed\"\n        src=\"/static/f09cdbe3746c7fadf665fd9ce1c76e8a/5a190/lighting_shader_diffuse_completed.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f09cdbe3746c7fadf665fd9ce1c76e8a/772e8/lighting_shader_diffuse_completed.png 200w,\n/static/f09cdbe3746c7fadf665fd9ce1c76e8a/e17e5/lighting_shader_diffuse_completed.png 400w,\n/static/f09cdbe3746c7fadf665fd9ce1c76e8a/5a190/lighting_shader_diffuse_completed.png 800w,\n/static/f09cdbe3746c7fadf665fd9ce1c76e8a/c1b63/lighting_shader_diffuse_completed.png 1200w,\n/static/f09cdbe3746c7fadf665fd9ce1c76e8a/29007/lighting_shader_diffuse_completed.png 1600w,\n/static/f09cdbe3746c7fadf665fd9ce1c76e8a/9b29b/lighting_shader_diffuse_completed.png 3840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>만약 실습을 진행하는데 어려움이 있는 경우에는 미리 완성된 다음 프로젝트 파일을 다운로드 받은 뒤 렌더몽키를 통해 열고 직접 분석해보도록 한다: <a href=\"https://github.com/sungkukpark/shader_programming_intro/blob/master/samples/lighting_shader_diffuse/lighting_shader_diffuse.zip\">다운로드 받기</a></p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Shader] Pope Kim의 셰이더 프로그래밍 입문 (4): 난반사광 조명셰이더"},"excerpt":"본 포스팅은 Pope Kim의 『셰이더 프로그래밍 입문 (한빛미디어, 2012)』의 Part 1의 Chapter 4에 해당하는 내용(p. 93-10…"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/shader_programming_intro_4/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216","63159454"]}